snippet.title: Warhammer: Age Of Sigmar - Temptestfall Cinematic Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase
snippet.description:
World Premiere of Warhammer: Age Of Sigmar - Temptestfall

Battle the forces of Nighthaunt in this VR-exclusive action-adventure Warhammer Age of Sigmar game using a variety of melee weapons, powerful staves, and immersive motion-based abilities and magic.

Coming to PC VR and Oculus Quest in 2021
